# 'segmented' speakers are those that we don't know their IDs, but we can at least segment them as distinct speakers.
# eg this speaker talks multiple times in this conversation, and we can tell that it's the same person, but we don't know their name.
2:45:21.28||meta|{"begin_speaker": "segmented:spk-4"}
2:45:21.28|2:45:22.24|text|What
2:45:22.24|2:45:22.88|text|do
2:45:22.88|2:45:23.36|text|you
2:45:23.36|2:45:23.68|text|think
